		<a name="cont"></a>
		<table width="500">
			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">All Contacts:</span></td>
				<td>
					The  All Contacts form shows all contact details that visitors entered via the Contact Us page of the web site.<br><br>
					
					You can search for any contacts by using the Search form.<br><br>
					
					You can decide how many contacts to be displayed on one page by selecting the entries per pages option.<br><br>
					
					You can sort the contacts by clicking the appropriate field title.<br><br>
					
					To send an email to a particular contact click the email icon next to the contact.<br><br>
					
					To delete a particular contact press the Del button in the Action field.<br><br>
					
					To compose and send a new message press the New Message button.
				</td>
			</tr>
			
			<tr height="5"><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		<a name="mail"></a>
		<table width="500">
			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Mails:</span></td>
				<td>
					The Info Requests form shows all requests for info made by visitors via the Contact form. The requests are grouped into categories.<br><br>
					
					To send mail to a group of visitors press the Send Info button.<br><br>
					
					You can view all mails you have sent by clicking the View button in the Action field.<br><br>
					
					To delete a particular sent mail press the Del button in the Action field.
				</td>
			</tr>
			
			<tr height="5"><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		<a name="fbk"></a>
		<table width="500">
			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Feedbacks:</span></td>
				<td>
					The Feedbacks form shows all contacts made by visitors that have feedbacks (questions). The feedbacks also indicate which section the visitors are interested in (from f1 to f6).<br><br>

					You can sort the contacts by clicking the appropriate field title.<br><br>
					
					To reply to a particular contact press the Reply button in the Action field.<br><br>
					
					To delete a particular contact press the Del button in the Action field.
				</td>
			</tr>
						
			<tr height="5"><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
			
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" align="center"><input type="button" value="Close" onclick="self.close()"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>
